Modules and PIP
module means using the code written by others in our code in this case we use modules
Modules are of 2 types 
1.Built in modules --------> These are the built in modules in the python 
2. external Modules-----> these are the modules written and developed by others and we use them

PIP ----> PIP installs packages

what ever the files or packages that we need will be installed in python using the pip 
comments escape sequences and print statements

comments --------> # is for single line cmment and """ """ this is for multi line comments
escape sequences---> 
\n for new line
\t for tab space
\\ for backslash (a\b)
\" for double quotes
\' for single quotes

